c: 34
v: 23
t: "Lan ora ana gunane syafa'at ana ngarsane Allah, kacoba barang wong kang wis diaprengake oleh syafa'at mau, malah besuk yen wong kang arep duwe syafa'at wis ilang wedine lan girising atine banjur padha tinakon, \"Allah Pangeran sampeyan, ngandika punapa?\" Kang tinakonan mangsuli, \"Allah ngandika kaliyan nyata\", Allah punika Maha Luhur tur Agung"